# Mosquitto ACL 细粒度权限
# mosquitto 2.x 语法: topic [read|write|readwrite|deny] <topic>

# ESP32 设备：只能发自己设备的数据，订阅自己的 cmd
user esp32cam
topic write cam/+/frame
topic write cam/+/env
topic write cam/+/status
topic read cam/+/cmd

# Flutter App：订阅所有设备的数据和状态，可下发 cmd
user app
topic read cam/+/frame
topic read cam/+/env
topic read cam/+/status
topic write cam/+/cmd

# Node.js 后端：订阅全部用于入库
user api
topic read cam/#

# 模式匹配（$SYS 系统主题默认只读）
pattern read $SYS/#
